*
*   This include lets you easily display a credit for a resource or image
*
*   You can use the following kinds of credits:
*
*    - unsplash
*    - hgb-member (TODO)
*    - other      (TODO)
*
*   For unsplash you'll need two extra parameters
*     name: a full name of the photographer
*     username: the username both present in the credit credit badge without the "@"
*
*   For hgb-member you'll need
*     mens: the item name from site.data.mensen
*
*       {% include credits unsplash name="David Werbrouck" username="bigkids" %}
*       {% include credits hbg-member mens="bmadou" %}
*
{% endcomment %}
